00:55:19,670 --> 00:55:24,380
Why do you keep talking about things from a decade ago?

812
00:55:24,380 --> 00:55:28,350
To be more specific, we didn't fight. I just took it all.

813
00:55:28,350 --> 00:55:31,300
If we had fought properly, maybe...

814
00:55:35,420 --> 00:55:36,790
You'll have a beer, right?

815
00:55:36,790 --> 00:55:39,160
I have mugs cooling in the fridge.

816
00:55:39,160 --> 00:55:40,680
Okay.

817
00:55:42,650 --> 00:55:45,170
I got both fried and marinated chicken.

818
00:55:46,510 --> 00:55:48,510
So?

819
00:55:48,510 --> 00:55:51,910
She said if we were a real family, we would have papers.

820
00:55:51,910 --> 00:55:53,920
She said I was a fake sibling.

821
00:55:53,920 --> 00:55:56,850
Wow. You heard all that from Hae Joon's ex-girlfriend?

822
00:55:56,850 --> 00:55:58,260
Right?

823
00:55:58,260 --> 00:56:00,200
So I told her

824
00:56:00,200 --> 00:56:03,400
I don't need validation from a piece of paper.

825
00:56:03,400 --> 00:56:06,950
I don't think the legal adoption is as important as I thought.

826
00:56:12,570 --> 00:56:14,160
Drumstick.

827
00:56:35,510 --> 00:56:37,980
Hey, isn't this a little weak?

828
00:56:37,980 --> 00:56:40,640
She even got called a fake sister.

829
00:56:44,320 --> 00:56:46,100
That's right.

830
00:56:48,430 --> 00:56:51,510
Stop making my surprise feel meaningless.

831
00:56:52,380 --> 00:56:54,910
Don't you ever do anything wrong?

832
00:56:55,590 --> 00:56:59,280
A surprise? What surprise?

833
00:57:10,490 --> 00:57:13,050
Ta-da!

834
00:57:13,050 --> 00:57:16,740
Do you want to have this and stop being angry? Or do you want to skip it and stay angry?

835
00:57:16,740 --> 00:57:18,410
I'll stop. I'll stop!

836
00:57:18,410 --> 00:57:21,760
I'm not angry anymore. I haven't been angry in a while!

837
00:57:23,260 --> 00:57:25,360
Just like that?

838
00:57:29,840 --> 00:57:32,500
Don't get it all over your face.

839
00:57:35,010 --> 00:57:37,360
I'm fine.

840
00:57:55,080 --> 00:57:57,310
Not you!

841
00:57:57,310 --> 00:57:59,650
Fine, fine.

842
00:58:04,990 --> 00:58:07,300
   

843
00:58:09,490 --> 00:58:12,170
- Have some. 
 - What is it?

844
00:58:13,170 --> 00:58:15,280
You were so brave yesterday.

845
00:58:15,280 --> 00:58:19,790
I was shocked and fumbling, but you stepped in and said, "No."

846
00:58:19,790 --> 00:58:23,110
It's hard to defend yourself on your own.

847
00:58:36,970 --> 00:58:41,760
So I don't know if you remember, but...

848
00:58:43,050 --> 00:58:47,620
Remember the thing you said you'd repay me for?

849
00:58:47,620 --> 00:58:50,830
Yes! Of course, I do.

850
00:58:50,830 --> 00:58:54,190
What are you thinking? I'll do everything I can.

851
00:58:55,700 --> 00:59:00,070
Can you take me to the next basketball game?

852
00:59:00,070 --> 00:59:03,290
You must go cheer him on as his sister.

853
00:59:03,290 --> 00:59:05,930
"Basketball"? Why would I go to basketball?

854
00:59:05,930 --> 00:59:08,500
It's no fun.

855
00:59:13,930 --> 00:59:15,890
But why?

856
00:59:15,890 --> 00:59:18,480
Think again!

857
00:59:18,480 --> 00:59:20,960
No. Never!

858
00:59:20,960 --> 00:59:23,140
Hey! Think again!

859
00:59:23,140 --> 00:59:24,270
- Are you going home? 
 - Bye!

860
00:59:24,270 --> 00:59:26,770
Bye. Take care.

861
00:59:27,500 --> 00:59:30,160
Hey, Hae Joon, come here for a second.

862
00:59:30,160 --> 00:59:33,840
- Go ahead. 
 - Bye!

863
00:59:34,950 --> 00:59:37,100
The digital camera you dropped off with us,

864
00:59:37,100 --> 00:59:39,840
the owner came to pick it up.

865
00:59:39,840 --> 00:59:40,950
Just like that?

866
00:59:40,950 --> 00:59:43,500
Yes. He was looking for someone.

867
00:59:43,500 --> 00:59:45,420
The photos looked normal.

868
00:59:45,420 --> 00:59:51,030
The principal told me to give it to him and get his contact info, so I did.

869
00:59:51,030 --> 00:59:53,220
   

870
00:59:53,220 --> 00:59:54,790
- So you know. 
 - Okay.

871
00:59:54,790 --> 00:59:56,660
Bye now.

872
01:00:02,730 --> 01:00:04,690
 Didn't you say your mom is in Seoul? 

873
01:00:04,690 --> 01:00:07,150
 Maybe your mom sent him. 

874
01:00:22,470 --> 01:00:24,000
Mom...

875
01:00:37,200 --> 01:00:38,890
Mom!

876
01:00:40,930 --> 01:00:42,400
What?

877
01:00:43,150 --> 01:00:45,120
I was mistaken.

878
01:00:45,120 --> 01:00:47,430
- I'm sorry. 
 - What was that?

879
01:00:47,430 --> 01:00:49,390
I'm sorry!

880
01:01:07,650 --> 01:01:09,930
Aren't you Joo Won's friend?

881
01:01:10,590 --> 01:01:14,000
Yes. H-Hello.

882
01:01:14,800 --> 01:01:16,320
Dal, right?

883
01:01:16,320 --> 01:01:19,480
Yes, I'm Dal.

884
01:01:22,600 --> 01:01:25,300
- Did you just hear that? 
 - No.

885
01:01:26,970 --> 01:01:30,110
Okay. Good, then.

886
01:01:42,810 --> 01:01:44,410
Pardon?

887
01:01:46,930 --> 01:01:49,260
If you didn't hear it, instead of "No,"

888
01:01:49,260 --> 01:01:51,810
you would have said, "What," right?

889
01:01:58,920 --> 01:02:01,090
Dal, do you have a minute?

890
01:02:07,290 --> 01:02:08,850
Dal, do you have hand tremors?

891
01:02:08,850 --> 01:02:11,600
Yes, it's severe.

892
01:02:19,340 --> 01:02:20,840
Eat.

893
01:02:21,740 --> 01:02:23,790
Thank you.

894
01:02:29,760 --> 01:02:32,110
Remember the movie where they go into space,

895
01:02:33,950 --> 01:02:36,570
shoot light, and erase people's memories?

896
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:45,750
If I had that, I wouldn't have to say all this.

897
01:02:49,320 --> 01:02:51,450
Oh, right.

898
01:02:57,210 --> 01:02:59,610
You heard, right?

899
01:02:59,610 --> 01:03:01,970
The mom thing?

900
01:03:01,970 --> 01:03:03,400
Yes.

901
01:03:04,760 --> 01:03:09,020
About that... Can you pretend like it didn't happen?

902
01:03:11,560 --> 01:03:15,630
If you tell Joo Won that I grabbed a passerby

903
01:03:15,630 --> 01:03:19,750
and yelled, "Mom!",

904
01:03:19,750 --> 01:03:22,760
I would be very upset.

905
01:03:23,630 --> 01:03:25,640
Okay. What?

906
01:03:25,640 --> 01:03:27,390
"Upset"?

907
01:03:28,000 --> 01:03:30,570
Do you mean upset?

908
01:03:30,570 --> 01:03:33,270
Yes. Upset.

909
01:03:44,630 --> 01:03:47,480
Dad, what are you making? It doesn't smell like broth.

910
01:03:47,480 --> 01:03:51,470
Cartilage. The stove at home isn't strong enough.

911
01:03:51,470 --> 01:03:54,410
It's tasty if I make it on the restaurant stove.

912
01:03:54,410 --> 01:03:56,780
It's Kang Hae Joon's favorite again.

913
01:03:56,780 --> 01:04:00,500
He plays sports! He needs to eat well.

914
01:04:02,020 --> 01:04:03,440
It isn't just for Hae Joon.

915
01:04:03,440 --> 01:04:05,740
San Ha, you should have some, too.

916
01:04:05,740 --> 01:04:07,180
Yes.

917
01:04:08,950 --> 01:04:13,250
Don't you feel like we are Kang Hae Joon's parasites sometimes?

918
01:04:15,060 --> 01:04:19,310
Last time, he let only Kang Hae Joon drink the spring water.

919
01:04:20,770 --> 01:04:24,270
I drank some of that, too.

920
01:04:33,660 --> 01:04:36,580
   

921
01:05:07,280 --> 01:05:10,860
See? They're done.

922
01:05:10,860 --> 01:05:16,120
Just wait. Let me set something up soon.

923
01:05:18,670 --> 01:05:20,650
I don't understand it, but...

924
01:05:20,650 --> 01:05:23,660
Class President, if it's what you want,

925
01:05:23,660 --> 01:05:27,800
I hope what your heart wants comes true.

926
01:05:27,800 --> 01:05:31,310
Let's go. Lunch is almost over.

927
01:06:00,020 --> 01:06:01,940
Who...

928
01:06:05,990 --> 01:06:09,970
Are you Kang Hae Joon?

929
01:06:11,030 --> 01:06:12,610
Yes.

930
01:06:14,550 --> 01:06:16,790
What are you doing?

931
01:06:17,750 --> 01:06:20,970
I'm your...

932
01:06:22,430 --> 01:06:24,540
your...

933
01:06:24,540 --> 01:06:28,650
I'm... your father.

934
01:06:28,650 --> 01:06:31,470
I'm your dad!

935
01:06:31,470 --> 01:06:34,130
Father!

