01:07:30,280 --> 01:07:33,420
 If you follow me to the U.S., you can do anything you want. 

949
01:07:33,420 --> 01:07:37,260
 How can you be sure good intentions will lead to good results? 

950
01:07:37,260 --> 01:07:38,760
 Don't tell Dad or Joo Won. 

951
01:07:38,760 --> 01:07:41,120
 I disappointed you all this time, right? 

952
01:07:41,120 --> 01:07:43,030
 I'll try to forgive you, too. 

